<i>noun</i>: 평자 [평ː자], 평론가 [평ː논가], 비평가 [비ː평가] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평자 [평ː자]</dt><br>
<dd>critic; reviewer</dd><br>
<dd>글이나 예술 작품 등을 비평하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who criticizes a piece of writing, a work of art, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평론가 [평ː논가]</dt><br>
<dd>critic; reviewer</dd><br>
<dd>평론을 전문으로 하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who criticizes, judges, or reviews professionally.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비평가 [비ː평가]</dt><br>
<dd>critic; reviewer</dd><br>
<dd>비평을 전문으로 하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who criticizes, judges, or reviews professionally.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>